the demand for housing, services, dining, and transportation arise. Little evidence on human gains in the post-ATe Has trade liberalization in this industry had positive im pacts on human development? Human gains were minimal in the post-ATC experiences of the four LOCs. Employment A", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "c24731e7-2227-470a-8c23-ec12e985f68d": {"__data__": {"id_": "c24731e7-2227-470a-8c23-ec12e985f68d", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/looking-beyond-export-gains-human-development-linkages-garment-industry-asian-ldcs-joint-policy-brief-issue-1", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Looking beyond Export Gains: Human development linkages in garment industry of Asian LDCs - Joint Policy Brief Issue 1", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/looking-beyond-export-gains-human-development-linkages-garment-industry-asian-ldcs-joint-policy-brief-issue-1", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "fd9b94f78212c18ff4d30cc4783976c98b2d1a7a22fd526c787c3c0c323f02b6"}, "3": {"node_id": "89cfaa0a-466a-4ade-a0ff-f20377a361ca", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/looking-beyond-export-gains-human-development-linkages-garment-industry-asian-ldcs-joint-policy-brief-issue-1", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "0de6eebbb551d91828affb977c47bad12e47b626eb9201262b70fa20ac7502b2"}}, "hash": "2c2