nmental Conservation The design of the BTFEC at a Glance The role of the BTFEC in financing environmental conservation in Bhutan The BTFEC has played a specific role in supporting environmental conservation in Bhutan. Apaper written by a director of the BTFEC in 2001 mentioned that, soon after the establishment of the BTFEC, the trust fund was expected to finance the recurrent costs of government\u2019s conservation programs, particularly for", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "699f11ea-bc3e-4ac6-b657-30f174acb3b4": {"__data__": {"id_": "699f11ea-bc3e-4ac6-b657-30f174acb3b4", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/national-climate-fund-case-study-report-bhutan-trust-fund-environmental-conservation", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "National Climate Fund Case Study Report: Bhutan Trust Fund for Environmental Conservation", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/national-climate-fund-case-study-report-bhutan-trust-fund-environmental-conservation", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "325bb50385e294ff4eeb7f534a58931b6aa0ddaa909ddbe40dfd59c147d25f7a"}, "3": {"node_id": "bbb8e839-d245-42c1-8931-2e1024ca5105", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/national-climate-fund-case-study-report-bhutan-trust-fund-environmental-conservation", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "275680594b7b91cb0a0287d